item.title: Naruto vs DBZ!
item.description: Naruto vs Dragon Ball Z! Yes, You guessed it right. It’s the comparison between naruto vs Dragon Ball Z in the world of anime. It is true that even though most of you have already watched Naruto, Naruto Shippuden and Boruto, I haven’t even finished my Naruto series. But now I regret, why I didn’t watch this amazing series that pumps my blood even in the most sensual, non-action scenes.
